Stress of Kentucky Bluegrass.

Chen Y(1), Chen Y(2)(3), Shi Z(4), Jin Y(5), Sun H(6), Xie F(7), Zhang L(8).

Author information:
(1)College of Horticulture and Landscape Architecture, Northeast Agricultural 
