University, Harbin 150030, China. chenyang8368215@hotmail.com.
(3)College of Life Science, Agriculture and Forestry, Qiqihar University, 
Qiqihar 161006, China. chenyang8368215@hotmail.com.
(4)College of Horticulture and Landscape Architecture, Northeast Agricultural 
University, Harbin 150030, China. shizj95516@163.com.
(5)College of Life Science, Agriculture and Forestry, Qiqihar University, 
